on rpi:
ros2 launch turtlebot4_bringup lite.launch.py

On laptop:
ros2 launch turtlebot4_navigation slam.launch.py
ros2 launch turtlebot4_viz view_robot.launch.py

on laptop: To save the map
ros2 service call /slam_toolbox/save_map slam_toolbox/srv/SaveMap "name: data: 'Robot51Map1'"

Visualization on Laptop:
rqt_graph
ros2 topic list
ros2 node list

watch -n 1 ros2 topic list (continuous monitoring)
watch -n 1 ros2 node list (continuous monitoring)
